dia harus dihabisi.

158
00:10:42,790 --> 00:10:43,910
Akkun.

159
00:10:44,790 --> 00:10:47,430
Di antara kita, kaulah yang
paling memikirkan teman, ya.

160
00:10:48,020 --> 00:10:49,600
